  "title": "S4 Full Stack Developer (Ref 25357)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities<br />• Design, build and configure applications to meet business process and application requirements.<br />• Prepare detailed technical design documents for requirements to be implemented.<br />• Prepare, conduct and document application unit testing results.<br />• Lead the effort to design, build and configure applications, acting as the primary point of contact.<br />• Support incident investigation fix and documentation for issue resolution.<br /><br />Requirements<br />• Degree / Diploma in Computer Programming with at least 3-4 years experiences<br />• Experienced in the following:<br />1. SAP FIORI (Enhancement and development) <br />2. Core Data Services (CDS) (Enhancement and development with authorisation) <br />3. ABAP on HANA </p><p>Good to have skills:</p><p>1. ABAP RESTful Application Programming Model (RAP)<br />2. IDOC, Web Service and OData<br />3. SAP Workflow (Classic/Flexible)<br />4. Standard Report (ALV, OOP)- Design, build and configure applications to meet business process and application requirements</p><p>Licence no: 12C6060</p>",
